items.title: Want to play ball?
items.description:
leadingedgephotography posted a photo:

January 16, 2013
016/365

I purchased Hera a couple of new toys, and when I gave them to her, she carried around them both for awhile. Then she decided the soccer ball was her favorite, this is her 'it's mine, stay away' face I think.

In post production, I set out to do a little color correction but that quickly turned into experimenting and playing around. I am not sure if I like the processing but it's different.
